articles.author: Molly Hunter
articles.title: Matildas mania grips Australia as women’s team captures hearts of World Cup host - NBC News
articles.description: Women’s World Cup co-host Australia has developed a national obsession with its team, the Matildas, who face England in the semifinal on Wednesday.
articles.content:
SYDNEY, Australia Nothing could compete with the Matildas. 
Meetings were canceled. Other sporting events, rescheduled. Pubs stocked up and viewing centers across the capital set up massive screens … [+1625 chars]
